{
  "stem": "1338.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a very cold winter, and there was an old, bearded Jew walking next to us in his wagon, dragging something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he turned to my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since Jews particularly are inclined to contemplation and philosophizing, he says to my father, look, he says, my life is obviously worth nothing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why am I doing this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father says, look at this philosopher.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's got himself time now to philosophize.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, you know, this is the moods, and this is the types of situations that you are involved.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are doing both.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You are attaining sanity and doing insane things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say six weeks to two months.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And because my street was already-- probably where I came from probably was out of bounds for Jews by then.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, schools immediately started.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, again, moved around, one building then another.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think three buildings eventually wound up in the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had-- part of the ghetto had a little bit of free land, open land, because there was-- they included the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Jewish cemetery was outside after some free space of fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so that's where the school eventually wound up, which was nice because there were some trees, you know, a nice environment, but first we were in a building in the center of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So school immediately continued.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, they tried to keep the school going all the time with interruptions, of course, whether it's a week or three weeks or whatever.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't recall dates.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we continued the school, and when the ghetto closed, we already were in the school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was going to school, so the daily life was built around it.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
